ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢寫係咁寫，係咪真係查唔知...<br />\n<br />\n買咗飛仲未坐。"},{"pid":"b68783d4e6d9d0ff4c191f2157825e98708a6e68","tid":297048,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗，佢官網教曬<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.china-airlines.com/tw/zh/fly/prepare-for-the-fly/information-for-travellers/Notice-for-Credit-Card-Payment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.china-airlines.com%2Ftw%2Fzh%2Ffly%2Fprepare-for-the-fly%2Finformation-for-travellers%2FNotice-for-Credit-Card-Payment&d=lkD6EmgsIG4G%2FZMb9TgwzNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=cb724d92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.china-airlines.com/tw/zh/fly/prepare-for-the-fly/information-for-travellers/Notice-for-Credit-Card-Payment</a><br />\n但都係大包圍，寫到用卡就要check</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次用PAYPAL 會穩陣啲<br />\n<br />\n未必次次旅行都帶晒所有卡出去，無帶買票果陣就仆街。<br />\n<br />\n好多時用邊張卡買嘢都係睇要儲咩分，有時買完都唔記得啦。"},{"pid":"c083679a02e7afffea4902994408bf92e2149a7e","tid":297048,"uid":48195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔該哂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4db7ef8d4478e70bb3c2778fc2e1d3f70803f69","tid":297048,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"睇邊間公司<br />\n長榮好似好嚴<br />\n某d 就如果係用經驗證既信用卡就唔洗出示<br />\n詳情都係問返航空公司好d"},{"pid":"c561ea288e866eb585dc5bc3928e68e954362f2f","tid":297048,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇邊間公司<br />\n長榮好似好嚴<br />\n某d 就如果係用經驗證既信用卡就唔洗出示<br />\n詳情都係問返航空公司好d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快運都話要查，佢買票唔洗做VISA 認証，都可能係咁麻鬼煩。<br />\n<br />\n中華已經係認証咗，但都要你提供張實物卡先上得機。"},{"pid":"f121721726b6414c7b29a1eb0634530f9fc240e